        "rich_text_K7VVfe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Cocktail looks are the sweet spot between casual and formal, not too underdressed and not as over-the-top as red carpet looks. They appear polished for evening events, with minimalism as the key. Think sleek dresses made of satin, silk, or crepe. Now imagine diamond jewelry that complements such elegant outfits. Jewelry has the power to elevate your look, if done correctly. Minimalist jewelry helps to pull this off without overshadowing your outfit. Let’s explore the right pieces to elevate your cocktail look:</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_CRWFAy": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Green Gemstone And Round Diamond Trilogy Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Green Gemstone And Round Diamond Trilogy Ring</h2>",
            "custom_id": "trilogy",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_rpLxeD": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Minimalist_Jewelry_Ideas_to_Elevate_Your_Cocktail_Look.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Minimal yet unique and captivating, this trilogy ring features a green center stone with two round diamonds on the side. <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/trilogy-engagement-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Trilogy Rings\">Trilogy Rings</a> symbolize the past, present, and future. Sometimes the trilogy ring is worn to represent a family with parents and a child. </p>",
            "layout_direction": "row",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "adaptive",
            "show_products": false,
            "products": []
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Dg3Xbi": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>In a romantic relationship, the trilogy ring is a dream ring because it represents all three: friendship, love, and fidelity. In this cocktail ring, the green gemstone signifies growth, renewal, balance, and prosperity. In some cultures, green gemstones are worn to ward off negative energy and bring lasting love and fortune.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
