            "content": "<p>Pair it with a necklace and <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/all-earrings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Lab Grown Diamond Earrings\">earring</a> set, stack it with a watch, or wear it alone. Each creates a refined look. </p>",
